title: Open Tues 7:45-8pm, 1BR/1B,Sh Laundry,Pets(736 Washington #7)
posting_body: ['1BR/1BA Apartment', '* $2,395/month annual lease', '* Shared laundry', '* WalkScore 100', '* TransitScore 100', '* Pet considered', '*', 'Available:', 'Now', 'OPEN HOUSE: Tuesday(8/2) 7:45pm-8pm', 'Address:736 Washington #7', 'Modern, quiet, off street 1BR/1BA apartment in the Financial District across from Portsmouth Square Plaza.', 'Building is on the edge of Chinatown, three blocks from the start of North Beach and three from the Transamerica Pyramid.', 'Floors are hardwood in the living room, bedroom is carpeted, and bath has tile.', 'Open living room has kitchen in a corner along two walls.', 'It has a skylight as well as a dining space with two windows.', "Kitchen's all stainless appliances include a gas stove and dishwasher.", 'It has granite counters, good cabinet space including some doors with glass panes.', 'Bedroom has a closet with sliding mirror doors and a skylight.', 'Bath is shower-over-tub with sliding glass doors.', 'Building includes coin-operated laundry.', 'Neighborhood has leased parking nearby.', 'Walk and Transit scores are 100.', 'Public transportation options are excellent and include bus lines 1, 8, 10, 12, 30, and 45.', 'Pet considered.', 'All your shopping and dining needs within easy walking distance.', "Tenant pays a one-time broker's fee.", 'Everest Mwamba', 'DRE# 01717299', 'Kenney & Everest Real Estate', 'DRE# 01984640', 'show contact info', 'office', 'Apply at KenneyandEverest .', 'com', 'Leasing and Real Estate: Our Family Business for Over 100 Years.', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.']
